data.description: Picture perfect, modern brick home! Inside, the charm continues with hardwood floors that grace every corner of this remarkable home. The interior has been thoughtfully designed with the perfect layout, offering three generously sized bedrooms that ensure everyone has their own space plus an additional two in the guest house steps away from the main home. The living room, with its spacious elegance, seamlessly flows into an inviting dining area adjacent to the kitchen with included smart stainless steel appliances, making mealtime a breeze. Picture yourself in the cozy four-seasons room just off the kitchen. It features a fireplace that sets the scene for memorable gatherings. The bar area is an entertainer's dream, where you can host friends and family with style including access to the backyard for gatherings. What sets this unique property apart is the loft space above the garage, an ideal spot for extended family or a home office. Imagine the convenience of working from home while still being close to the comforts of your living space. This property is perfectly positioned, just minutes away from I-94, with easy access to 162nd Street, I-294, and Lincoln Highway. Your daily commute will be a breeze, allowing you to enjoy more of what you love. With its updated features and prime location, this home is just missing your personal touch. Schedule your private showing today!
